{"tid":2224008,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃之鋒古思堯涉去年10月非法集結　准保釋12月再提堂","createTime":"2020-09-30T08:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T09:02:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71ef4af342d9336fc98e9485f0687090f72665b1","tid":2224008,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒及社運人士古思堯，被控去年十月參與非法集結等罪名，在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒及古思堯先後抵達東區裁判法院。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月5日，港島區舉行反蒙面法遊行，兩人被控明知而參與未經批准集結；黃之鋒同時被控違反禁止蒙面規例，在集結期間使用掛耳式口罩。控方要求兩名被告答辯，遭辯方反對，指高院十一月將就禁蒙面法進行司法覆核聆訊，裁決對本案有影響，要求將案件押後。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官批准將案押後至12月18日再提堂，兩人獲准以一千元擔保外出，黃之鋒不得離開香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=407450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407450&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyhmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=e4b2435f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407450&h=0936c86a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=407450</a>"},{"pid":"b7fa1020e376815346544eb63d7a0115e40b6df5","tid":2224008,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e244e9f12358c62cb4fbc7c0e46d4975279fd3","tid":2224008,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"e147f0a190b179e0cc40dafdfec463787474b2de","tid":2224008,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}